entries.waypoint_description_2: A patrol from Colonel Zarvold's Imperial Army battalion on Rori, equipped with a thermal detonator sought by Booto Lubble, Gungan liaison to the Zephyr Base Alliance outpost.

entries.return_waypoint_description_1: Gungan liaison to the Zephyr Base Alliance outpost on Rori, currently waiting for an Imperial rank cylinder that he wants to add to a necklace.

entries.npc_5_1: My be sweetin' on de commando trainer here, Raxa Binn. Shesa mooie-mooie! My tinkin' shesa likin' a necklace made of Empire rank cylinder tings.

entries.npc_1_1: Heydo! My workin' on makin' a necklace from Empire officer rank cylinder tings. My knowin' 'bout a warrant officer in de wilds wit some soldiers. My wantin' you to be killin' de warrant officer an' bringin' mesa hisa rank cylinder ting. Hey?
